{"tid":307860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【MV發佈】究竟人生嘅意義係咩？ 原：《有時》","createTime":"2017-07-03T16:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T10:04:09.000Z","uid":61750,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7d31151d38f8ad296e5a4161ff2fa3df217e1c","tid":307860,"uid":61750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:20:02.000Z","msg":"可能人生的確未必一定要有意義<br />\n與其諗人生有咩意義<br />\n不如開開心心咁過好每一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁其實係咪就係我人生嘅意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主唱：周國賢<br />\n作曲：周國賢<br />\n原詞：小克<br />\n編曲：周國賢<br />\n監製：周國賢．Goro@heearmusic<br />\n<br />\n改詞：困獸鬥<br />\n主唱：流觴<br />\n<br />\n我努力向前 我拼命向前<br />\n哪裏是我終點線<br />\n時日又荏苒 瞬間數十年<br />\n於盲目裡征戰<br />\n<br />\n人生的意義就似零 背棄着姓名<br />\n勝仗沒有歡笑聲<br />\n這分針 沒風聲<br />\n時針已隨年月結冰<br />\n<br />\n*<br />\n到處漂 到處闖<br />\n仍然是海浪<br />\n身處大霧裏 混沌裏<br />\n已漸覺淒愴<br />\n要到逹何處海港<br />\n未知的方向明暸開朗<br />\n#<br />\n<br />\n濾鏡抺清 盼看清一片藍圖星宿<br />\n找到那北斗有沒有<br />\n只好任意飄流 飄到遠方星球 <br />\n尋覓那觸不到的遠埠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界幻變時 我腳步變移<br />\n找不到中心標誌 <br />\n情人或應試 理想與鑰匙<br />\n怎釐定那主次<br />\n<br />\n迷失於那熱鬧廢城 進退亦叫停<br />\n轉世讓細胞覺醒<br />\n痛哭聲 狂歡聲<br />\n來生與明月共細聽<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *#<br />\n<br />\n濾鏡抺清 盼看清一片藍圖星宿<br />\n找到那北斗有沒有<br />\n只好任意飄流 飄到遠方星球<br />\n將一切的瑣碎都帶走<br />\n<br />\n沒有半山單位以及美色的優勢<br />\n匆匆一世遇上千樣問題<br />\n友敵勝敗散聚冷暖<br />\n愛恨集齊再各散東西<br />\n<br />\n到處漂 到處闖<br />\n仍然是海浪<br />\n等到大霧散 混沌過 <br />\n也是太虛妄<br />\n那怕蕩回避風港<br />\n也會沒法避開拍岸驚駭巨浪 <br />\n<br />\n濾鏡抺清 已看清一片藍圖星宿<br />\n天邊那北斗正合奏<br />\n織女望向牽牛 相思對方橋頭<br />\n從牢獄裡繼續眼觀星空的變奏 <br />\n天體的搏鬥<br />\n轉世或不久<br />\n有時注定眾生艱苦跟富有<br />\n分隔或廝守<br />\n一瞬或不朽<br />\n最終也躲不過毒咒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s3rcnYyoWUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs3rcnYyoWUk&d=h1MB3VLklj48%2BH4sCaN85b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=58265b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s3rcnYyoWUk</a>"},{"pid":"d6afa7771c690acb2755e7b293cf562098a018e9","tid":307860,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e804b2c1748de121df440611a9fffd17f3dd406","tid":307860,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"正啊LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec880af058433511dee5b4cae0bc017efa413884","tid":307860,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b794ee13ba89adaffd9f358e7858aea500d3a47","tid":307860,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f792d901c1dafe167464ba68197f3fcdfd3e229b","tid":307860,"uid":61750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ce954168bfebe7decabf9ad5fc0f6a32fc9ae3","tid":307860,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T19:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好正既詞"},{"pid":"b149a4aaa6cb21b8d0dec4fe09e7206a95601a4a","tid":307860,"uid":61750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ddb27ba309ab24b5cf750b61b9bceab47f74d2","tid":307860,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets